
``showGiottoImageNames``
============================

showGiottoImageNames

Description
-----------

Prints the available giotto images that are attached to the Giotto object

Usage
-----

.. code-block:: r

   showGiottoImageNames(gobject)

Arguments
---------

.. list-table::
   :header-rows: 1

   * - Argument
     - Description
   * - ``gobject``
     - a giotto object


Value
-----

prints names of available giotto image objects
